[ music ]

00:08.383 --> 00:09.592
- Haha y'know I mean,

00:09.676 --> 00:10.927
that's why some people

00:11.010 --> 00:12.429
{\an8}have to wear a helmet
in the shower.

00:12.512 --> 00:14.431
{\an8}- Makes sense,
it makes sense dude,

00:14.514 --> 00:15.974
{\an8}it makes sense.

00:16.056 --> 00:17.100
- Now Kid Danger and I
are gonna be live-streaming

00:17.183 --> 00:19.602
for about another
20 minutes, sooo...

00:19.686 --> 00:20.687
- Yep. And...

00:20.770 --> 00:24.274
the name of our next
video caller is...

00:24.357 --> 00:25.150
J.D.!

00:25.233 --> 00:29.404
{\an8}- Hm, J.D.
Could be initials.

00:31.030 --> 00:33.158
- There's only one way
to find out.

00:33.241 --> 00:35.702
- Hey Captain Man
and Kid Danger! It's--

00:35.785 --> 00:38.413
- Uh, sorry about that--

00:38.496 --> 00:41.124
{\an8}seems like we had
a technical problem there.

00:41.207 --> 00:43.460
- Why does he keep
disconnecting me?

00:43.543 --> 00:46.546
- Probably 'cuz you
keep calling him.

00:46.629 --> 00:48.798
- Alright, we got
another video caller

00:48.882 --> 00:52.427
who goes by the name...
"Mister E. Person."

00:52.510 --> 00:55.430
{\an8}- Ooo, "Mister E. Person."

00:56.973 --> 00:59.851
- It is I!
Doctor Minyak!

00:59.934 --> 01:02.020
{\an8}- Ohhhh, Mystery Person,
I get it.

01:02.103 --> 01:02.979
{\an8}- Yeah.

01:03.062 --> 01:04.147
{\an8}- What do you want, Minyak?

01:04.230 --> 01:08.026
- To challenge you,
Captain Man!

01:08.109 --> 01:09.194
- He wants to challenge you.

01:09.277 --> 01:09.986
- Uh-huh. Challenge accepted.

01:10.069 --> 01:11.946
- Wh-but you don't even know

01:12.030 --> 01:13.156
what my challenge is.

01:13.239 --> 01:14.407
- Don't care.

01:14.491 --> 01:16.576
'Cuz I can
beat you at anything.

01:16.659 --> 01:17.994
- Yeah, soooo...

01:18.077 --> 01:20.163
{\an8}what is your "big challenge"
for Captain Man?

01:20.246 --> 01:22.207
{\an8}- Yeah, whaddaya
wanna lose to me at?

01:22.290 --> 01:24.417
- Oh, I shan't lose.

01:24.501 --> 01:27.170
Because I challenge you,
Captain Man,

01:27.253 --> 01:30.256
to a contest of SPELLING!

01:32.091 --> 01:33.843
{\an8}- Spelling?

01:33.927 --> 01:36.179
- Yesss. Perhaps you know

01:36.262 --> 01:37.722
that Swellview's
Yearly Spelling Bee

01:37.806 --> 01:39.682
takes place next Friday!

01:39.766 --> 01:41.184
- Uh-ohhhh...

01:41.267 --> 01:42.519
- Wait, where ya goin'?!?

01:42.602 --> 01:45.480
{\an8}- Shhhh. When ya gotta go,
ya gotta go.

01:47.190 --> 01:49.651
- You and I shall both
enter the Bee,

01:49.734 --> 01:53.238
and when it's over,
the entire world shall see

01:53.321 --> 01:55.198
which of us is the winner,

01:55.281 --> 01:57.909
and which is a looooserrrrr.

01:57.992 --> 01:59.536
- Uhhh...
- Fine! Let's do it!

01:59.619 --> 02:01.246
- Uhhh no, I'm sorry,
can you please hold.

02:01.329 --> 02:02.705
- Huh, what?
- Move, move move.

02:02.789 --> 02:04.290
- Why ya pushin' me?

02:04.374 --> 02:06.000
- Ray! You can't spell!

02:06.084 --> 02:08.211
- Whaddaya mean
I "can't spell?"

02:08.294 --> 02:09.628
[ elevator dings ]

02:09.711 --> 02:10.880
- I mean, I've read
your texts and emails

02:10.964 --> 02:12.048
and you're a terrible speller.

02:12.131 --> 02:13.508
- Uhh you guys...?
- Just a second.

02:13.591 --> 02:15.802
I find your comments offensive.

02:15.885 --> 02:17.011
- Well I'm sorry!

02:17.095 --> 02:18.972
- You're just mean
to me sometimes.

02:19.055 --> 02:20.223
- Alright. Okay.
Spell "sometimes."

02:20.306 --> 02:22.058
- What?!?
- Spell "sometimes."

02:22.141 --> 02:25.353
- Okay. S...
- All right. Mm-hm.

02:25.436 --> 02:25.895
- U...
- Wrong.

02:25.979 --> 02:28.064
- Right. What?

02:28.147 --> 02:29.149
Well that was a tricky one!

02:29.232 --> 02:30.316
- It really wasn't dude.

02:30.400 --> 02:32.318
- Hey, can I please
say something?!?

02:32.402 --> 02:34.112
- What what?!?
- Yes, what what what what?

02:34.195 --> 02:36.281
- You can't do this!
- Why?

02:36.364 --> 02:39.075
- 'Cuz! I'm gonna be
in the Spelling Bee.

02:39.158 --> 02:40.535
- You?

02:40.618 --> 02:42.412
- Yeah, I've won the last
three years in a row

02:42.495 --> 02:44.247
and if I win this year,
I'll be the first

02:44.330 --> 02:46.749
Swellviewian ever to win
four years straight!

02:49.460 --> 02:52.297
- Ohhh, Charlotte.

02:52.380 --> 02:55.466
Charlotte, Charlotte,
Charlotte...

02:55.550 --> 02:56.676
do you ever think about
anybody but yourself?

02:56.759 --> 02:59.137
- Wh-what?

02:59.220 --> 03:00.305
- I can't have
this one thing?

03:00.388 --> 03:02.432
- He just wants this
one thing.

03:02.515 --> 03:03.266
- And you, as my friend,
you won't let me have

03:03.349 --> 03:04.267
just one moment in the sun,

03:04.350 --> 03:06.352
to beat Doctor Minyak
at spelling?

03:06.436 --> 03:08.688
- Just one sunny moment.

03:08.771 --> 03:11.316
- But the guidance
counselor at school said

03:11.399 --> 03:12.609
it would be great
for me if I--

03:12.692 --> 03:13.985
- Great for YOU.

03:14.068 --> 03:16.112
See? For YOU.

03:16.195 --> 03:19.240
Must it ALL be
about YOU Charlotte?

03:20.700 --> 03:22.660
- Okaaay.
Fine, I'm sorry.

03:22.744 --> 03:24.996
- I hope so.

03:30.501 --> 03:31.961
- Hi, we're back.

03:32.045 --> 03:33.087
- It's about time!

03:33.171 --> 03:34.797
- And I accept your challenge...

03:34.881 --> 03:36.716
so, what's the bet?

03:36.799 --> 03:38.968
- The bet is...

03:39.052 --> 03:41.220
whichever of us loses
the Spelling Bee...

03:41.304 --> 03:42.764
must ride
a child's tricycle...

03:42.847 --> 03:44.641
all the way
from Swellview...

03:44.724 --> 03:47.060
to California
and back!

03:47.143 --> 03:47.977
- I was not expecting that...

03:48.061 --> 03:50.313
- Yeah, pretty weird bet, dude.

03:50.396 --> 03:51.898
- But I ain't
gonna lose, so...

03:51.981 --> 03:54.859
You got a bet, Minyak.

03:54.943 --> 03:57.278
- Ah, lovely!

03:57.362 --> 03:59.739
And you just wait,
Captain Man.

03:59.822 --> 04:01.491
You will lose.

04:01.574 --> 04:03.076
And while you're tricycling

04:03.159 --> 04:06.829
to California and back
I shall--

04:06.913 --> 04:08.665
- Ha!

04:08.748 --> 04:10.291
He had more to say
but you didn't care.

04:10.375 --> 04:11.709
- Nope.

04:11.793 --> 04:13.378
- Well, I guess I'll just
call the Bee Board

04:13.461 --> 04:15.838
and tell 'em I'm not gonna
compete this year.

04:15.922 --> 04:17.339
- Nah, no no no no!
- No no no, no.

04:17.423 --> 04:18.716
- Don't do that!

04:18.800 --> 04:20.301
- But I thought you
don't want me to win?

04:20.385 --> 04:21.511
- I don't.
- He doesn't.

04:21.594 --> 04:22.804
- I want you to lose
on purpose,

04:22.887 --> 04:24.305
so I can win.

04:24.389 --> 04:25.264
- Okay.

04:25.348 --> 04:27.475
- And you can help

04:27.558 --> 04:30.019
make sure that Minyak
doesn't cheat.

04:30.103 --> 04:31.312
- Wait wait wait wait
wait wait wait...

04:31.396 --> 04:32.021
You're a terrible speller.

04:32.105 --> 04:34.274
How are you gonna win?!?

04:34.357 --> 04:36.567
- Oh, I'm gonna cheat.
- He's gonna cheat good.

04:38.444 --> 04:39.195
- It all just kinda happened.

04:39.278 --> 04:40.363
I wanted an after-school job.

04:40.446 --> 04:42.907
But then,
an indestructible superhero

04:42.991 --> 04:44.617
hired me to be his sidekick.

04:44.701 --> 04:45.576
- Ah!

04:45.660 --> 04:46.661
- Now we blow bubbles...

04:46.744 --> 04:48.371
and fight crime.
Feels good.

04:48.454 --> 04:49.998
[ theme music ]

05:02.802 --> 05:04.303
{\an8}- Call it.
- Up the tube!

05:05.054 --> 05:07.932
{\an8}- Aw, my boot!
- Ha!

05:09.350 --> 05:11.310
[ music ]

05:16.649 --> 05:17.734
- Hey Trent, Mary,

05:17.817 --> 05:19.068
you're on in about 12 seconds.

05:19.152 --> 05:20.069
- Thanks.

05:20.153 --> 05:21.487
- Hello! My name
is Mary Gaperman,

05:21.571 --> 05:26.826
{\an8}and this is Swellview's
42nd annual Spelling Bee!

05:29.162 --> 05:31.414
- We're live in
four, three, two...

05:31.497 --> 05:32.749
[intro music plays]

05:32.832 --> 05:35.376
- Hello and welcome!
I'm Trent Overunder,

05:35.460 --> 05:40.339
and this is Swellview's
42nd annual Spelling Bee!

05:45.011 --> 05:48.639
- This year, we have five
bright, young finalists.

05:48.723 --> 05:50.975
And also, oddly,
two adult men.

05:52.977 --> 05:53.936
First, Swellview's
very own superhero,

05:54.020 --> 05:57.273
Captain Man.

05:57.356 --> 05:59.609
[ cheers and applause ]

05:59.692 --> 06:02.612
- Go Captain Man!

06:02.695 --> 06:05.907
Oh, and Charlotte.

06:07.533 --> 06:08.534
- And our final contestant
is four-time

06:08.618 --> 06:12.663
convicted felon,
Doctor Horatio T. Minyak!

06:12.747 --> 06:16.793
{\an8}[ boos and hisses ]

06:17.335 --> 06:18.252
- Stick around,

06:18.336 --> 06:20.963
because after this short break,

06:21.047 --> 06:23.424
we'll BEE right back.

06:25.802 --> 06:28.846
- Okay everybody, we're back
live in two minutes!

06:31.390 --> 06:32.517
- All right, yo,

06:32.600 --> 06:34.185
before we go in, let's
do a quick cheat check.

06:34.268 --> 06:36.687
- Cheat check.
Let's do it.

06:36.771 --> 06:38.064
- So...

06:38.147 --> 06:38.981
if we want Ray to say
the letter G...

06:39.065 --> 06:40.108
what starts with G?

06:40.191 --> 06:43.111
- Uhh...Guh-rapefruit.

06:43.194 --> 06:45.863
- Yeah, yeah yeah,
good good good good.

06:49.659 --> 06:53.162
- Okay, so if we want
Ray to say the letter E...

06:53.246 --> 06:55.665
you hold up annnn...

06:55.748 --> 06:57.166
- Egg.
- Nice.

06:57.250 --> 07:00.503
- Alright dude,
let's uhh...go...

07:00.586 --> 07:03.297
I...N.

07:03.381 --> 07:05.383
- Aha!

07:05.466 --> 07:06.843
O! K!

07:06.926 --> 07:08.553
- Ahh!

07:10.721 --> 07:12.306
- Hey.
- Hey.

07:12.390 --> 07:14.559
- Could I have
some a'that ketchup...

07:14.642 --> 07:15.893
to put on my finger?

07:15.977 --> 07:17.937
- Nooo!

07:18.020 --> 07:18.646
- Get outta here, guy.

07:21.023 --> 07:23.317
What are you sucking
your finger for?

07:30.908 --> 07:31.868
- Oh hey,
hey Piper, perfect.

07:31.951 --> 07:32.618
- Yeah hi.

07:32.702 --> 07:34.036
- Hey uhh...can you uhh...

07:34.120 --> 07:35.037
sit on that side,

07:35.121 --> 07:36.747
so me and Jasper
can sit together?

07:36.831 --> 07:39.208
- No.
- What? N-no?

07:39.292 --> 07:40.543
But me and Jasper
wanna sit together.

07:40.626 --> 07:42.378
- Not my problem.

07:42.461 --> 07:43.671
- But we were just gonna--
- You're just--

07:43.754 --> 07:46.132
- Ten seconds everyone,
please take your seats now.

07:46.215 --> 07:47.884
- Piper just move!
- Hey, hey, hey.

07:47.967 --> 07:49.427
- I'm not gonna!!
- Why does that matter?

07:49.510 --> 07:50.636
- Henry it's all right,
we can just split up,

07:50.720 --> 07:52.388
- Ah fine fine fine fine!

07:52.471 --> 07:54.015
- All right.

07:54.098 --> 07:54.891
- Pardon me...
comin' though...

07:54.974 --> 07:58.936
Sorry...sorry.

07:59.020 --> 08:01.105
- In four, three, two...

08:01.189 --> 08:02.732
- And we are back,
here at the

08:02.815 --> 08:04.066
Swellview Spelling Bee

08:04.150 --> 08:06.110
where things are just
about to get under way!

08:06.194 --> 08:07.486
- That's right Trent.
And as is tradition,

08:07.570 --> 08:10.907
the first word goes
to the winner

08:10.990 --> 08:15.203
of last year's Spelling Bee,
Sherlock Paggy.

08:18.039 --> 08:20.875
- It's Charlotte Page.

08:20.958 --> 08:22.835
It's the same every year.

08:22.919 --> 08:25.463
- Okay Charlotte.

08:25.546 --> 08:26.380
Your word is...

08:26.464 --> 08:32.345
Imbecile.
Imbecile.

08:32.428 --> 08:34.679
- Imbecile.

08:34.764 --> 08:38.808
I-M-B-E-C-I-L-E.
Imbecile.

08:38.893 --> 08:41.270
- That is correct.
[ding]

08:47.193 --> 08:49.403
Okay, next up is...
Carlos Calderone.

08:53.282 --> 08:55.326
Carlos, your word is--

08:55.409 --> 08:56.202
- Schwoz to Henry
and Jasper...

08:56.285 --> 08:59.288
Schwoz to Henry and Jasper...

08:59.372 --> 09:01.666
are you guys
ready for a sound check?

09:01.749 --> 09:02.083
- Yup go.

09:02.166 --> 09:06.045
- Okay.

09:06.128 --> 09:09.632
HEY!!!
THIS IS A SOUND CHECK!

09:09.715 --> 09:12.718
Woman: I cried and cried
until my mother gave in

09:12.802 --> 09:17.890
and bought be a souvenir
from the gas station.

09:17.974 --> 09:19.809
- Shhhh.
Carlos.

09:19.892 --> 09:23.187
- S-o-u-v-e-n-i-r.
Souvenir.

09:23.271 --> 09:25.356
- Correct!
[ding]

09:26.399 --> 09:29.485
- Ooo, way to go, Carlos.

09:29.568 --> 09:32.989
- Okay, and now we have
Doctor Minyak.

09:33.072 --> 09:34.657
[crowd boos]

09:38.369 --> 09:40.830
- [ faintly ]
I'm rea--

09:40.913 --> 09:43.833
Oh...I'm ready.

09:43.916 --> 09:46.252
- Terrific. Your word is...

09:46.335 --> 09:48.504
Prodigious.
Prodigi--

09:48.587 --> 09:54.093
P-R-O-D-I-G-I-O-U-S.
Prodigious.

09:54.176 --> 09:57.680
And that was CORRECT!

09:57.763 --> 10:01.350
- Hey! I'm the one who
gets to say if it's correct.

10:04.520 --> 10:04.979
That is correct.

10:05.062 --> 10:07.356
[ding]

10:09.608 --> 10:12.111
- Now to spell his
first word of the Bee...

10:12.194 --> 10:12.737
Captain Man.

10:18.492 --> 10:20.745
[cheers]

10:22.538 --> 10:25.875
- Your word is:
Hypotenuse.

10:25.958 --> 10:28.878
- Ah, of course.

10:25.958 --> 10:28.878
Hypotenuse.

10:28.961 --> 10:31.505
Similar to the rhinoceros.

10:31.589 --> 10:36.302
Uh I believe hypotenuse
is spelled...

10:36.385 --> 10:38.804
- H!

10:38.888 --> 10:41.057
- Honey...H.

10:41.140 --> 10:45.895
- Y.
- Y.

10:45.978 --> 10:48.022
- P.
- P.

10:48.105 --> 10:50.983
- O.
- O...

10:51.067 --> 10:53.778
- T.
- T.

10:53.861 --> 10:56.280
- E.
- E...

10:56.364 --> 11:00.201
- N.
- N...

11:00.284 --> 11:03.162
- U.
- U...

11:03.245 --> 11:05.915
- S.
- S.

11:05.998 --> 11:08.542
- E.

11:10.503 --> 11:11.754
- E.

11:11.837 --> 11:13.255
- Yes!

11:13.339 --> 11:15.466
- Hypotenuse.

11:15.549 --> 11:17.760
- That is quite correct.
[ ding ]

11:17.843 --> 11:19.762
[ cheers ]

11:26.268 --> 11:30.106
- M-O-N-T-A-G-E.
Montage.

11:30.189 --> 11:31.440
[ ding ]

11:31.524 --> 11:35.694
- F-L-A-M-B-E.
Flambe.

11:35.778 --> 11:38.531
[ ding ]

11:38.614 --> 11:39.240
- Good!

11:39.323 --> 11:42.785
- M-O-N-I-U-M.

11:42.868 --> 11:43.869
Dulibbamonium.

11:43.953 --> 11:46.330
[ buzzer ]

11:47.331 --> 11:48.332
- Just a moment...

11:48.416 --> 11:51.794
S-U-B-T-E-R-F-U-G-E.

11:51.877 --> 11:53.504
Subterfuge. Thank you.

11:53.587 --> 11:55.631
[ ding ]

11:55.714 --> 11:57.675
Yes, I just got
another one right!

11:59.760 --> 12:02.847
- I-A-L!

12:05.224 --> 12:06.434
Marsupial!

12:06.517 --> 12:06.767
[ ding ]

12:10.104 --> 12:13.441
- B-L-A-F-H-E-R-W--

12:13.524 --> 12:15.151
Oh!

12:15.234 --> 12:16.944
- Wrong! He said O!

12:17.027 --> 12:18.195
But the next letter is H!

12:18.279 --> 12:20.322
So he's wrong!
Now, buzz him out!

12:20.406 --> 12:22.158
Buzz him!

12:22.241 --> 12:23.826
[ buzzer ]

12:23.909 --> 12:27.037
- P-U-S-I...

12:27.121 --> 12:29.665
L-L-A-N--

12:29.748 --> 12:32.626
- Owwww!

12:32.710 --> 12:35.921
- I-M-O-U-S.
Pusillanimous.

12:36.005 --> 12:36.338
[ ding ]

12:36.422 --> 12:37.256
- M...

12:37.339 --> 12:41.010
- U.
- U.

12:41.093 --> 12:42.386
- M.
- M...

12:42.470 --> 12:45.431
Chrysanthemum!

12:45.514 --> 12:46.891
[ ding ]

12:46.974 --> 12:49.393
[ cheers ]
- Yes!!

12:51.812 --> 12:54.398
- N-A-U-G--

12:57.943 --> 13:00.654
- You're next.

13:01.739 --> 13:04.200
- Isabella, please
finish the word.

13:04.283 --> 13:06.452
- Uhhh... what was
my word again?

13:06.535 --> 13:08.496
- Sorry, we're not allowed
to refresh your memory.

13:08.579 --> 13:11.874
Mary...
[ buzzer ]

13:15.336 --> 13:16.504
- And we're finally down

13:16.587 --> 13:19.381
to our final three
final finalists!

13:25.679 --> 13:27.223
- We sure are, Mary.
But since it's been

13:27.306 --> 13:28.807
five hours since
we took a break,

13:28.891 --> 13:31.060
if anyone would like
to visit the restroom,

13:31.143 --> 13:33.521
now would be a--

13:36.148 --> 13:37.775
- I'm starving.
Gimme some of your food.

13:37.858 --> 13:39.151
- No no no no,
what are you doin'?!?

13:39.235 --> 13:39.902
- Dude?!?

13:39.985 --> 13:41.904
- You can't eat my apple!

13:41.987 --> 13:44.240
- Fine, then gimme the egg.

13:44.323 --> 13:45.241
- Nooooooo,
are you insane?!? Okay,

13:45.324 --> 13:47.284
A and E are two
of this country's

13:47.368 --> 13:49.286
most popular vowels!

13:49.370 --> 13:50.246
- What are you saying?
- Hey... hey...

13:50.329 --> 13:52.498
No loud talking
in the auditorium.

13:52.581 --> 13:54.792
- Yeah yeah, fine.
- We're very sorry.

13:55.834 --> 13:58.379
- Now gimme a snack!
- No no! Piper!

13:58.462 --> 13:59.505
- Will you stop
being so stingy?!?

13:59.588 --> 14:03.926
[ blows whistle ]

14:04.009 --> 14:05.511
- Go on, show 'em the door.

14:05.594 --> 14:07.263
- Wh-what?!?
- Oh c'mon, seriously?!?

14:07.346 --> 14:08.347
- But, no...
she was taking my stuff!

14:08.430 --> 14:10.307
This is my stuff!
- Hey whoa-whoa...

14:10.391 --> 14:11.016
hey hey wh-what's
going on here?!?

14:11.100 --> 14:11.892
- We're being evicted!

14:11.976 --> 14:14.019
- What?
- I wanted one egg! One!

14:19.692 --> 14:23.195
- Uh.. hey hey hey hey.

14:23.279 --> 14:25.531
Hey, hey, hey, hey...

14:25.614 --> 14:26.657
guy, what are ya doin'
eating my stuff!

14:26.740 --> 14:27.950
- Oh yeah, I thought you left.

14:28.033 --> 14:29.785
- What do you mean
you thought I left,

14:29.868 --> 14:31.620
what does that...
what are you doi--

14:31.704 --> 14:32.830
Awww, you opened my yogurt--

14:32.913 --> 14:33.497
why would you
open my yogurt man?

14:33.581 --> 14:34.957
- To dip the carrot.

14:35.040 --> 14:38.210
- What is that?
What is that right there?

14:38.294 --> 14:39.295
Is that powdered sugar?!?

14:39.378 --> 14:41.880
Did...did you
eat my DONUT?!?

14:41.964 --> 14:44.800
- Yeah, and your pear.

14:44.883 --> 14:46.885
- What?

14:46.969 --> 14:49.513
AWWWWWWWWWW!!!

14:52.516 --> 14:54.310
- And we're back again!

14:54.393 --> 14:56.812
[ ding ]

14:56.895 --> 14:59.440
- We started
with seven spellers.

14:59.523 --> 15:01.025
Now, four of them
have been defeated.

15:01.108 --> 15:04.403
They're gone.
And only three remain,

15:04.486 --> 15:05.362
to compete for the coveted
Swellview Spelling Bee trophy.

15:05.446 --> 15:08.907
- C'mon Schwoz...

15:08.991 --> 15:09.783
[ phone rings ]

15:09.867 --> 15:12.494
- Hellooooo,
I am Schwoz.

15:12.578 --> 15:14.288
- Hey Schwoz, man,
we have a big problem!!!

15:14.371 --> 15:15.831
- What happened?!?

15:15.914 --> 15:17.875
- Jasper got thrown
outta the Spelling Bee, and...

15:17.958 --> 15:20.169
and some guy ate
a bunch of my foods!

15:20.252 --> 15:23.047
- Then how are you going
to help Ray spell words

15:23.130 --> 15:25.341
he's too stupid to spell
by himself?!?

15:25.424 --> 15:26.634
- That's the problem!

15:26.717 --> 15:29.470
Look if we can't help Ray spell,

15:29.553 --> 15:31.847
then we gotta find a way

15:31.930 --> 15:33.307
to make Doctor Minyak lose!

15:33.390 --> 15:34.558
- Ooo, I know what to do!

15:34.642 --> 15:36.685
- What?!?
Tell me. Tell me.

15:36.769 --> 15:41.065
- Okay, after Doctor Minyak

15:41.148 --> 15:42.566
spells his next word...

15:42.650 --> 15:45.110
you stand up
and challenge the spelling!

15:45.194 --> 15:46.862
- But if he spells it right,
why should I challenge it?!?

15:46.945 --> 15:49.406
- Because I'm going to change

15:49.490 --> 15:50.658
the spelling of whatever
word he spells!

15:50.741 --> 15:54.328
- Dude you can't change
the spelling of a word!!!

15:54.411 --> 15:57.998
- Ha ha. Yes I can.

15:58.082 --> 15:59.333
- How?!?

15:59.416 --> 16:01.293
- With the internet.

16:01.377 --> 16:02.628
- Wh...you're gonna change

16:02.711 --> 16:04.838
the spelling of a word
on the entire internet?

16:04.922 --> 16:07.883
- Yah, if you will
let me hang up this telephone.

16:07.966 --> 16:09.510
- Alright okay okay, bye!

16:09.593 --> 16:10.552
- Challenge the spelling!

16:10.636 --> 16:11.595
- I got it, I will,
okay hang up!

16:11.679 --> 16:14.973
- Noooo, you hang up first.

16:15.057 --> 16:16.392
- Oh my god!

16:16.475 --> 16:17.559
- Doctor Minyak.

16:17.643 --> 16:20.688
[crowd boos]

16:23.148 --> 16:23.899
Okay Doctor Minyak,

16:23.982 --> 16:27.569
your word is...
Zeitgeist.

16:27.653 --> 16:31.323
- Zeitgeist.
Z-E-I-T-G-E-I-S-T.

16:31.407 --> 16:33.158
Zeitgeist.
Chaaaa!

16:33.242 --> 16:35.035
- Correct!
[ ding ]

16:37.579 --> 16:41.375
- Wait! I uhh...

16:41.458 --> 16:42.710
I challenge!

16:42.793 --> 16:47.172
[crowd gasps]

16:47.256 --> 16:47.965
- Uhhh young man...
Doctor Minyak

16:48.048 --> 16:50.509
spelled the word correctly.

16:50.592 --> 16:52.511
- Yeah. It's right here,

16:52.594 --> 16:54.596
in this dictionary book.

16:55.264 --> 16:56.932
- Right...but umm...

16:57.015 --> 17:00.602
the internet is way
more up-to-date

17:00.686 --> 17:02.855
than dictionary books...

17:02.938 --> 17:04.440
which are made from trees.

17:04.522 --> 17:08.193
Am I right?

17:08.277 --> 17:09.694
- Okay, L'Varb,
please check the spelling

17:09.778 --> 17:12.614
of "zeitgeist" online.

17:12.698 --> 17:15.409
- Almost...
almost...

17:15.492 --> 17:18.871
[ computers beeping ]

17:18.954 --> 17:21.582
- Okay, the correct
spelling of zeitgeist is

17:21.665 --> 17:24.877
Z-E-I-T-G-E-I-S-T...Q.

17:24.960 --> 17:27.921
- Q?!?
[ crowd gasps ]

17:29.131 --> 17:32.259
- Yes!

17:32.342 --> 17:33.635
- Ah yes...

17:33.719 --> 17:35.429
We can't forget the final Q...

17:35.512 --> 17:38.515
in the word zeitgeist-qua.

17:38.599 --> 17:41.059
- All right, it seems that our
dictionary-book is wrong,

17:41.143 --> 17:44.188
which means,
so is Doctor Minyak.

17:44.271 --> 17:45.981
- That's right Trent.

17:46.064 --> 17:48.859
[ buzzer ]
You're outta here!!!

17:48.942 --> 17:52.154
- Oh come on!
What sort of Bee is this?!?

17:52.237 --> 17:54.782
- It's the sort of Bee
that you just lost, Minyak.

17:54.865 --> 17:57.826
Better get your tricycle ready,

17:57.910 --> 18:01.246
to ride to California
and back.

18:01.330 --> 18:04.333
[ laughing ]

18:04.416 --> 18:06.210
- Yeah, Minyak!

18:11.548 --> 18:13.217
Yeah.

18:14.426 --> 18:16.637
Well excuse me, Captain Man,

18:16.720 --> 18:18.347
but you haven't
won this Bee yet!

18:18.430 --> 18:20.766
If that girl wins,
then you also lose,

18:20.849 --> 18:24.228
and you will have to pedal
with me to California...

18:24.311 --> 18:25.479
and back.

18:25.562 --> 18:27.815
- Oh yeah. Right.

18:27.898 --> 18:31.276
- Ha ha! Yesssss!

18:33.946 --> 18:34.863
- Okay, Captain Man.

18:34.947 --> 18:37.115
Your word to spell is...

18:37.199 --> 18:39.701
Pectoral.

18:39.785 --> 18:42.955
- Pectoral.
Okay no problem.

18:43.038 --> 18:44.122
I believe "Pectoral"
is spelled...

18:56.635 --> 18:58.011
Uhhh...
okay, I got this,

18:58.095 --> 19:01.974
I can do this,
okay uh...Pectoral.

19:02.057 --> 19:06.854
Well, obviously it starts
with a P...right?

19:06.937 --> 19:10.566
Followed by E?

19:10.649 --> 19:13.318
then...C.

19:17.489 --> 19:19.575
- C'mon

19:19.658 --> 19:23.620
- Um... T...

19:23.704 --> 19:27.165
uh...O...R...

19:27.249 --> 19:28.083
- Just two more
letters to go!!!

19:28.166 --> 19:30.836
- Hey, she can't
tell him that!

19:30.919 --> 19:33.380
- I'll allow it.

19:33.463 --> 19:35.340
- And the last two letters
of "pectoral" are...

19:40.220 --> 19:43.265
A...

19:56.987 --> 19:59.281
[ dramatic music ]

20:02.409 --> 20:06.038
[ cheers echo ]

20:13.337 --> 20:16.214
[ cheering ]

20:19.843 --> 20:23.347
[ cheers echoing ]

20:26.558 --> 20:27.142
W.

20:27.225 --> 20:29.436
- Wha--
- No.

20:29.519 --> 20:31.355
- Ahh!

20:33.148 --> 20:38.654
- Wrong!
You're Captain Wrong!

20:38.737 --> 20:40.948
[ buzzer ]

20:46.495 --> 20:47.287
Okay, Charlotte,

20:47.371 --> 20:48.664
if you can spell "Pectoral"

20:48.747 --> 20:50.165
then you win.

20:50.249 --> 20:54.795
- P-E-C-T-O-R-A-L.
Pectoral.

20:54.878 --> 20:56.338
- Correct!
[ ding ]

21:05.806 --> 21:06.390
- Thank you.

21:09.935 --> 21:13.939
- Well, Captain Man...

21:14.022 --> 21:16.525
- Whoah...
Yeah!

21:16.608 --> 21:17.818
- You're a good guy...

21:17.901 --> 21:23.323
who has to pedal a tricycle
to California and back.

21:23.407 --> 21:24.241
- Nahhhh.

21:24.324 --> 21:25.993
- C'mon dude,
you made a bet.

21:26.076 --> 21:28.120
- Yeah but...

21:28.203 --> 21:29.997
Minyak's not gonna really go
through with that. Y'know?

21:35.043 --> 21:37.337
- To California!

21:43.593 --> 21:44.803
- Alright, this is stupid.

21:44.886 --> 21:47.472
[ car horn honks ]

21:47.556 --> 21:50.892
- Ah, shut up!!!

